# CODEOWNERS - used to test Mergify's `github-code-owner-review-satisfied`.
#
# Paths listed here have an owner: a PR touching them stays unsatisfied
# until one of the owners approves it (the "match" case).
# Paths NOT listed here have no owner, so the attribute is vacuously
# satisfied (the "no match" case).

/frontend/   @sileht
/api/        @sileht
*.py         @sileht

# docs/ is intentionally left without an owner (negative test case).
